01:23:53,127 --> 01:23:56,867
Hi, I'm Michael.

979
01:24:31,363 --> 01:24:37,463
Now, I wanna tell you
a little secret

980
01:24:37,471 --> 01:24:42,471
about a great gift from god.

981
01:24:43,309 --> 01:24:45,179
This gift is a human emotion

982
01:24:45,178 --> 01:24:50,518
and considered destructive
by the enemies of god.

983
01:24:54,520 --> 01:24:55,950
Fear.

984
01:24:55,956 --> 01:25:02,025
You can never, never,
never stop

985
01:25:02,027 --> 01:25:04,867
fearing yourself.

986
01:25:04,864 --> 01:25:08,964
We are our own worst enemies.

987
01:25:08,968 --> 01:25:16,308
And we must fear ourselves till
the day we meet god himself.

988
01:25:16,808 --> 01:25:22,918
God didn't put us here to live
our lives in constant fear.

989
01:25:22,915 --> 01:25:23,815
No, of course not.

990
01:25:23,816 --> 01:25:27,815
And then he scolded me
for asking questions.

991
01:25:27,819 --> 01:25:29,279
Well, that's not fair.

992
01:25:29,287 --> 01:25:30,157
We're here to learn

993
01:25:30,155 --> 01:25:31,385
and we learn in part
by asking questions.

994
01:25:31,389 --> 01:25:34,789
No, we're here to serve god,
not to identify

995
01:25:34,793 --> 01:25:40,063
as the exact kind of christians
they want us to be.

996
01:25:41,098 --> 01:25:42,428
I'm sorry.

997
01:25:42,433 --> 01:25:43,333
Don't be.

998
01:25:43,334 --> 01:25:48,844
You know what's best
because that's god
speaking through you.

999
01:25:55,311 --> 01:25:58,411
You wanted to see me?

1000
01:25:58,815 --> 01:26:01,415
Now, you've been rallying
the students against us

1001
01:26:01,418 --> 01:26:06,488
as though you're
being controlled
by the devil himself.

1002
01:26:08,124 --> 01:26:11,494
I've learned a lot
about the Bible here,

1003
01:26:11,495 --> 01:26:12,935
and for that I thank you.

1004
01:26:12,930 --> 01:26:19,170
But I refuse to be controlled
by anyone other than god.

1005
01:26:19,169 --> 01:26:20,469
I follow my own path.

1006
01:26:20,470 --> 01:26:24,199
Yeah, and you want others
to follow you.

1007
01:26:24,906 --> 01:26:27,606
Perhaps it's best
if we mail you your diploma

1008
01:26:27,610 --> 01:26:31,480
and that you not attend
the ceremony.

1009
01:26:35,851 --> 01:26:39,051
I don't know if i
can stay here anymore.

1010
01:26:39,055 --> 01:26:41,625
Oh. Where will we go?

1011
01:26:43,391 --> 01:26:45,121
We?

1012
01:26:46,361 --> 01:26:51,131
Uh, I've been praying about it.

1013
01:26:51,133 --> 01:26:53,502
About us.

1014
01:26:53,501 --> 01:27:01,011
I told god how I feel about you
and how much you mean to me.

1015
01:27:01,009 --> 01:27:02,939
And you know what?

1016
01:27:04,980 --> 01:27:08,580
I was consumed
with nothing but peace.

1017
01:27:08,583 --> 01:27:11,923
Pure peace.

1018
01:27:15,123 --> 01:27:17,463
I love you.

1019
01:27:17,459 --> 01:27:20,059
I love you, too.

1020
01:27:52,925 --> 01:27:55,125
And be not conformed
to this world:

1021
01:27:55,128 --> 01:27:59,368
But be you transformed
by the renewing of your mind,

1022
01:27:59,365 --> 01:28:05,165
that you may prove
that good, glorious,

1023
01:28:05,171 --> 01:28:08,211
and perfect will of god.

1024
01:28:09,375 --> 01:28:13,545
That you may know that good,
acceptable,

1025
01:28:13,546 --> 01:28:16,276
and perfect will of god.

1026
01:28:45,109 --> 01:28:52,318
- Which would you prefer to have?
- Frosted flakes or fruit loops?

1027
01:28:52,316 --> 01:28:54,146
Well, obviously fruit loops.

1028
01:28:54,151 --> 01:28:55,381
Why? Why obviously?

1029
01:28:55,386 --> 01:28:58,156
Well, you're a fruit loop.

1030
01:29:17,706 --> 01:29:19,576
There you are.

1031
01:29:19,576 --> 01:29:21,646
Are you okay?

1032
01:29:22,344 --> 01:29:25,174
Yeah, I'm fine.

1033
01:29:29,785 --> 01:29:31,215
Okay, got 'em.

1034
01:29:34,623 --> 01:29:36,353
You get everything?

1035
01:29:36,359 --> 01:29:37,729
Mm-hmm.

1036
01:29:40,062 --> 01:29:43,492
These are going to storage.

1037
01:29:49,337 --> 01:29:53,777
Well, so you can have
a little more room
for your shoes?

1038
01:29:53,776 --> 01:29:54,446
Shut up.

1039
01:29:54,443 --> 01:29:57,473
I have never seen anyone
with more shoes than you.

1040
01:29:57,479 --> 01:30:00,439
You can never have
too many shoes.

1041
01:30:12,093 --> 01:30:14,363
Get those out of here.

1042
01:30:33,513 --> 01:30:34,543
Hello?

1043
01:30:34,549 --> 01:30:36,349
<i> Hi.</i>

1044
01:30:40,788 --> 01:30:43,287
Hi.

1045
01:30:45,091 --> 01:30:46,561
<i> How are you?</i>

1046
01:30:46,560 --> 01:30:48,690
Good.

1047
01:30:48,695 --> 01:30:50,765
I finished school.

1048
01:30:50,764 --> 01:30:54,604
But I'm no longer
on their path.

1049
01:30:55,534 --> 01:30:59,774
<i> So what path</i>
<i> are you on now?</i>

1050
01:30:59,773 --> 01:31:00,743
My own.

1051
01:31:00,740 --> 01:31:05,210
<i> I'm going to be the pastor</i>
<i> of my own church.</i>

1052
01:31:09,316 --> 01:31:12,155
