1053
01:31:12,151 --> 01:31:13,451
Um...

1054
01:31:14,752 --> 01:31:16,422
I, uh...

1055
01:31:16,422 --> 01:31:18,752
I got the picture
you sent of olly.

1056
01:31:18,757 --> 01:31:21,817
<i> I know it was months ago,</i>
<i> but I didn't respond.</i>

1057
01:31:21,827 --> 01:31:24,727
<i> So how is she?</i>

1058
01:31:25,798 --> 01:31:28,158
Oh, she's getting old.

1059
01:31:28,167 --> 01:31:29,497
But she's okay.

1060
01:31:29,502 --> 01:31:30,302
She has this

1061
01:31:30,302 --> 01:31:33,172
<i> stuffed animal that she</i>
<i> carries around with her now</i>

1062
01:31:33,172 --> 01:31:36,212
<i> everywhere she goes</i>
<i> like it's her baby.</i>

