Bennett...

1064
01:31:43,314 --> 01:31:47,454
I should tell you
before someone else does.

1065
01:31:47,452 --> 01:31:49,452
I'm engaged.

1066
01:31:49,820 --> 01:31:54,320
To a...
Really amazing woman.

1067
01:31:54,591 --> 01:31:57,291
Now, I know
what you're thinking because

1068
01:31:57,295 --> 01:31:59,725
<i> I asked myself the same thing--</i>

1069
01:31:59,731 --> 01:32:01,161
<i> am I really in love with her</i>

1070
01:32:01,166 --> 01:32:05,796
<i> or am I only doing this</i>
<i> to be right in god's eyes?</i>

1071
01:32:05,803 --> 01:32:11,342
<i> And I'm truly</i>
<i> in love with her, Bennett.</i>

1072
01:32:12,308 --> 01:32:15,948
God went to the root
of my same sex desires

1073
01:32:15,946 --> 01:32:17,646
and he uprooted them.

1074
01:32:17,648 --> 01:32:21,648
