that they were abnormal.

1075
01:32:21,652 --> 01:32:22,452
<i> Michael...</i>

1076
01:32:22,452 --> 01:32:27,292
<i> I'm really glad</i>
<i> you think you're happy.</i>

1077
01:32:28,758 --> 01:32:30,388
And I wish you all the best.

1078
01:32:30,394 --> 01:32:32,954
I really do.
I think you know that.

1079
01:32:32,963 --> 01:32:37,603
<i> But I have no idea</i>
<i> why you would call me up</i>

1080
01:32:37,601 --> 01:32:40,470
<i> and use words like "abnormal."</i>

1081
01:32:41,570 --> 01:32:46,210
<i> I'm so sorry for the way</i>
<i> that things went down.</i>

1082
01:32:46,209 --> 01:32:49,409
<i> But just because we don't</i>

1083
01:32:49,412 --> 01:32:50,312
share certain beliefs,

1084
01:32:50,313 --> 01:32:55,513
