we can't still be friends.

1085
01:32:57,719 --> 01:33:00,659
I'll always be your friend.

1086
01:33:02,257 --> 01:33:05,897
<i> And I really hope</i>
<i> that this path</i>

1087
01:33:05,895 --> 01:33:08,994
<i> takes you where you wanna go.</i>

1088
01:33:10,364 --> 01:33:13,464
But I also hope that...

1089
01:33:13,468 --> 01:33:16,538
As you're setting out
to help other people...

1090
01:33:16,538 --> 01:33:21,238
<i> That you really take some time</i>
<i> to help yourself.</i>

1091
01:33:23,944 --> 01:33:26,774
<i> I-i am. I...</i>

1092
01:33:26,781 --> 01:33:30,291
<i> I'm not gonna sit here</i>
<i> and say that I know</i>

1093
01:33:30,285 --> 01:33:33,855
<i> I'll be this way</i>
<i> for the rest of my life.</i>

1094
01:33:33,855 --> 01:33:37,524
We're always changing, evolving.

1095
01:33:37,524 --> 01:33:40,894
And I'm open to that.

1096
01:33:45,733 --> 01:33:47,893
Then...

1097
01:33:47,901 --> 01:33:52,371
I guess nothing's
really changed.

1098
01:33:52,373 --> 01:33:55,573
<i> Yeah.</i>

1099
01:33:55,775 --> 01:33:59,045
<i> You take care</i>
<i> of yourself, okay?</i>

1100
01:34:01,514 --> 01:34:04,344
